    Percy Rebecca

    Brynn also known as Percy Rebecca online, is a huge fan of children's TV Shows & Video-Games such as, Nintendo, Minecraft, Sailor Moon, LEGO Ninjago

    She has been making videos to his YouTube channel since the 1st of March 2013.

    She loves making videos for children & adults. Brynn has had many YouTube channels in the past. 

    She official YouTube channel is called @rebeccapercy

     

    Brynn is a British & French content creator.
